channel.title: Can someone PLEASE help me getting server up?
channel.description:
Ok, I'm doing exactly everything guides and people are telling me to do, but I just can't seem to get my server up. I've done the no-ip thing, press runserver, but every time I still can't log in, and I know it's offline because when I try to register it on the moparscape server status, it just sais it's offline. I turned off all my firewalls ext, and I'm using rickscape v5.
I AM ALSO USING A ROUTER (LINKSYS) IF THAT IS DOING ANYTHING.
So yah, please help, I really wanna get my pking server up since a lot right now are shitty/lagging 15 seconds per click. Also if you're advice works and you like pking servers, I'll give you mod if you want...
